org.batfish.coordinator.resources

Class ReferenceLibraryResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.coordinator.resources.ReferenceLibraryResource

  • @Produces(value="application/json")
public class ReferenceLibraryResource
extends Object
    The ReferenceLibraryResource is a resource for servicing client API calls for the address library. It is a subresource of ContainerResource.
